column2: b'Mikakunin de Shinkoukei: Kamoniku tte Midori-ppoi Aji ga Suru no ne.'

b'OVA included with special edition of volume 5 of the Mikakunin de Shinkoukei manga.\n\nMashiro and Kobeni share with each other a story from their pasts. Kobeni retells an episode of her childhood with Benio and Nadeshiko while Mashiro describes one of her days back on her home in the mountains.'
